  "texts": [
    "transforming to the frequency domain of the series.",
    "The second transformation based design pattern involves ensembles of pipelines, where each base pipeline consists of making repeated, different, transforms and using a homogeneous base classifier.",
    "TSC ensembles can also be heterogeneous, collating the classifications from transformation pipelines and ensembles of differing representations of the time series.",
    "The third common pattern involves transformations embedded inside a classifier structure.",
    "For example, a decision tree where the data is transformed at each node fits this pattern."
